{"tid":2411193,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英更新香港營商指引 指國安法損港人權 刪「國際金融中心」字眼","createTime":"2021-02-17T07:12:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T10:20:10.000Z","uid":54800,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"9c560eccbfae68c309aee7b1c27317f23b52788b","tid":2411193,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T07:12:24.000Z","msg":"英國外交部日前更新與香港的營商指引，由過去形容香港為國際金融中心貶為區域樞紐，並且刪去與港府有正面、前瞻性的關係等字眼，同時不再直接描述香港享有高度自治。<br />\n<br />\n據《眾新聞》報道，英國外交部自2019年8月後，本周二再度更新與香港的營商指引，而這次更涉及多個方面。<br />\n<br />\n新的指引特別提到《國安法》在港實施、《國安法》容許不公開審訊或送中審訊、4名民主派議員被取消資格、以及BNO簽證等內容，並且。。。。<br />\n。。。。<br />\n。。。<br />\n。。<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210217/3ECBVZ3X65DD3N2HMUXO6YD4KA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210217%2F3ECBVZ3X65DD3N2HMUXO6YD4KA%2F&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN2xckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=5171aa50\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210217%2F3ECBVZ3X65DD3N2HMUXO6YD4KA%2F&h=01336f92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210217/3ECBVZ3X65DD3N2HMUXO6YD4KA/</a>"},{"pid":"86a8c2b2c0cfe189efb92ba15e444b931171664f","tid":2411193,"uid":54800,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T07:13:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小區輸紐！"},{"pid":"8c9670b35b86a98d87c83e67fe71fbddc212d265","tid":2411193,"uid":72185,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T07:19:57.000Z","msg":"邱騰華：fuck you! 基本法腐乳"},{"pid":"860613b307841adf7174690941f92c13fbd0974b","tid":2411193,"uid":25240,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T07:21:38.000Z","msg":"真係日出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4cfea68ea39e251515a1f9782ad